  <div class="content">
    <ul class="menu clearfix"><li class="first leaf travel mid-4798"><a href="http://www.sonata-software.com/services/travel-it" title="">Travel</a></li>
<li class="leaf digital-engagement mid-4801"><a href="http://www.sonata-software.com/services/digital-engagement" title="">Digital Engagement</a></li>
